name: Michael Oklejewski
text: Matt did a great job. Service was fast, friendly and courteous plus the food was served fresh and hot! Would recommend this location.

text: Have not had Pizza Hut pizza for years. Since it was Easter and pour favorite was closed, we thought we would give it a try.  Deliver was extremely slow.  Took over an hour and fourth five minutes.  The pizza was cold!!  Will not give Pizza Hut another penny!,

text: Service was slow. Brought out wrong pizza and then threw the missing topping on.
